改變極少. 於是改為檢查每1秒之間的改變, 發現只有頭部和字幕有改變, 然後再試試檢測每6秒之間的改變, 竟然都沒有太大分別. 一個人能在幾分鐘, 身體接近沒有改變, 是極為可疑.</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">from Facebook: Jackie Cho</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"22d1c279d41e12b2f4a23471f3e8f9f527eed7b0","tid":1542760,"uid":121869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:22:39.000Z","msg":"我相信林鄭動議撤回條片係合成片段! 但點解?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1542639\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1542639</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aDOaJQg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaDOaJQg.jpg&h=dc6a2b3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以往政府嘅片唔會打&rdquo;製作&rdquo;,只有香港特別行政區政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗唔明個制作目的喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過DEEPFAKE換臉又好 一早錄定又好<br />\n記得追住831有人死左來問來追究。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n民族自強 港人自救<br />\n沒有暴徒 只有暴政<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\nFIVE DEMANDS - NOT ONE LESS"},{"pid":"588893ebf0dabbc45c4d2d2961a7d332980abeee","tid":1542760,"uid":303188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:22:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8c4fc885bd05fb9cfb0dfd1f7030c682fb17f9b5","tid":1542760,"uid":226421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T03:24:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/11/08/chinese-news-agency-ai-anchors/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2018%2F11%2F08%2Fchinese-news-agency-ai-anchors%2F&d=Fy0o8YzXie14Yexn7W6ruSaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=5ac9d1c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/2018/11/08/chinese-news-agency-ai-anchors/</a>"},{"pid":"55dd28557828f8b115394eada8b069686ce99f2e","tid":1542760,"uid":226421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c4fc885bd05fb9cfb0dfd1f703